title: Harry and [Y/N] Engagement
body:
MORE INSTAGRAM PIECES MY LOVES!! 

Liked by poppydeyes, livwyatt95, harryfan1 and 3254 others

yourinstagram So I decided to try @poppydeyes banana pop recipe from her AMAZING blog! Go show her some love because honestly, these are delicious and the blog itself is so amazing to look at and read through

View all 985 comments

livwyatt95 These look so good!! But next time use more chocolate woman 😉

gemmastyles These look GORGEOUS! I’m coming to pinch one!!

poppydeyes Oh my days these look amazing! Thank you for the love dear!! You should definitely write a blog by the way, you’re brilliant <3

yourinstagram @poppydeyes Do you fancy helping a gal out? I have no idea where to start!!!

poppydeyes @yourinstagram YES I’ll help!! I’ll DM you now <3

harryfan1 These look so good! Compromising between fruit and chocolate, I love it

y/nfan1 UMMMM, [Y/N] knows Poppy and reads the blog? That’s brilliant!!!

Add a comment…

Liked by zoesugg, harrystyles, harryfan1 and 3522 others

yourinstagram Is it too early to bring the iced coffees back? I hope not because these were to DIE FOR!!

View all 732 comments

livwyatt95 You are too aesthetically pleasing hun! Kills me off

harrystyles No it isn’t, but I’d appreciate no milk in my coffee thanks 😉

yourinstagram @harrystyles these are both mine, sweets. Yours wasn’t good enough for the picture 😉

zoesugg <3

harryfan1 This is so satisfying!!!

y/nfan1 I NEED THESE IN MY LIFE!!

nickgrimshaw Why do those glasses look like the ones you used to get from McDonalds when you ordered a certain meal? Is that just me?

harryfan2 @nickgrimshaw! Hahaha that’s too much!!!

harryfan3 OMG ZOELLA COMMENTED?! Whatttt?

Add a comment…

Liked by annetwist, gemmastyles, harryfan1 and 3645 others

yourinstagram Decided to surprise the babe at his gig today!! I promise you that he was rather excited to see me <3

View all 1214 comments

harrystyles The BEST surprise!!

gemmastyles He needs a haircut 😉

harryfan1 Aww this is too cute! What song was he singing?

y/nfan1 @harryfan1 he was singing Sweet Creature when he saw her! I was stood next to them!!

niallhoran He has me to thank for that guitar playing 😉

yourinstagram @niallhoran he told me to tell you to shove off 😉 But thank you for teaching him, it means I get to be serenaded 😊

harrystyles @yourinstagram I’ll serenade you whenever you please, baby

Add a comment…

Liked by zoesugg, livwyatt95, harryfan1 and 5312 others

yourinstagram Turned up at my mum and dads and the babes had made my favourite crispy potatoes!!! They’re the best!! (And very loved by H)

View all 3242 comments

harryfan1 These look so good!! Your mum is perfect <3

harrystyles Can you make them for me when we get home?! Honestly, they taste so good!!!!

livwyatt95 WHERE WAS MY INVITE FOR MAMA BAE’S CRISPY POTATOES?! I’m offended ☹

y/m/I @livwyatt95 I’ve saved you some! If you come tomorrow, I’ll cook them for you 😊

livwyatt95 @y/m/I OMG YOU’RE THE BEST! I LOVE YOU!!

zoesugg These look so good! I want them now 😊

yourinstagram @zoesugg I’m sure I can get my mum to write you the recipe! She loves sharing her food haha xx

zoesugg @yourinstagram Oh that would be lovely! Thank you! Xx

Add a comment…

Liked by harrystyles, liampayne, y/nfan1 and 5433 others

yourinstagram Everybody meet Rusty, my mum, dad and Jacob’s new dog! He’s the softest thing both physically and personality wise. I’ve spent at least an hour today just cuddling him!! <3

View all 2341 comments

livwyatt95 Babe he’s stunning!!

harrystyles He stole my missus ☹

yourinstagram @harrystyles No babe! I still love you more!!! You’re my puppy <3

gemmastyles I’m not a dog person but he is adorable and I want to steal him and hug him forever!

harryfan1 YOU AND HARRY SHOULD GET A DOG! You’d make great dog parents

y/nfan1 @harryfan1 It probably wouldn’t get on with Evie ☹

zoesugg I’m trying to not let Alfie see because he would want another dog!!!

yourinstagram @zoesugg You should get another dog! Nala would love a friend 😉

Add a comment…

Liked by gemmastyles, y/nfan1, harryfan1 and 4321 others

yourinstagram This bedroom at my parents’ house was mine from the ages of 0-20 and it’s done me good. I decorated it this way before I left for uni and my mum kept it! She’s the best

View all 3213 comments

harrystyles I’ve loved being in your childhood room sweetheart. It screams ‘you’ <3

livwyatt95 Many a sleepover were had in that room but now you have sleepovers with your fiancé! That’s too strange ☹

y/nfan1 That interior is amazing, very you and the fact that Harry knows is killing me

harryfan1 Aw this is so pretty!!! Bet Harry can’t wait to get into the bed with you 😉

zoesugg INTERIORS OF DREAMS!!! I love it! <3

gemmastyles You can tell that you got Harry to redecorate the guest room, because it’s so unbelievably you 😊

y/m/I It’s strange that you still get to come and stay in YOUR bedroom, but now you bring Harry and we love it even more <3

Add a comment…

Liked by y/nfan1, harryfan2, pixielott and 3242 others

yourinstagram When in London town…

View all 2532 comments

gemmastyles You’re such a tourist

livwyatt95 we lived in London for 3 years, why didn’t we do this together?!

harryfan1 This is so cute!! You and Gemma need to give Harry a lesson on how to do this!! Cause he’s crap!

harryfan2 This is so cute. How come you were in London?

yourinstagram @harryfan2 I had a meeting sweet, but on my way back I couldn’t help it haha

y/nfan1 This is brilliant! I want to do it!!!

Add a comment…

Liked by gemmastyles, y/m/I, livwyatt95 and 5343 others

yourinstagram Thanks @gemmastyles for the photo, not quite sure what to think of this outfit though!

View all 3243 comments

gemmastyles I like it!

yourinstagram @gemmastyles I think I would prefer it with a black jacket, or maybe a duster one? I dunno x

harrystyles You’re beautiful baby! Stunning!!!! <3 <3

y/nfan1 This is a lovely outfit! I like the idea of a darker jacket though <3

harryfan1 This looks lovely!!! You should definitely try with a darker jacket too xx

livwyatt95 GIRL YOU STUNNING!! But, wear a darker jacket with those jeans, or wear darker jeans <3 <3

y/m/I Gorgeous!

Add a comment…

Liked by harrystyles, harryfan1, y/nfan1 and 7635 others

yourinstagram xoxo

View all 2345 comments

harrystyles <3

harryfan1 OMG this is too cute!!

livwyatt95 Gossip Girl 

annestyles This is such a nice sentiment! xxx

yourinstagram @livwyatt95 THANK YOU FOR THAT! You’ve just made my day babe 

y/nfan1 This is so sweet, if anyone saw it they wouldn’t know that it’s a matching tattoo with a rock star ;)

Add a comment…

Thank you for the love on the Harry and [Y/N] series’!! It means the world and I love you all so much xoxo

title: Everything We Had
body:
Harry was there. Harry was always there, through everything. Until he wasn’t anymore. She was his best friend, she was the love of his life. She was also the girl he so stupidly let slip right out of his fingers.

Chapter Eleven

HarrySummer 2017 – LondonHarry held Elise until she cried herself to sleep, until the tears drained all the energy completely out of her, until her eyes fluttered shut and her breathing evened out….
